# WooCommerce POS Plugin (Free)

WordPress plugin enabling Point of Sale for WooCommerce. Free version on WordPress.org.

- Extends WooCommerce REST API for POS functionality
- Provides `/pos` endpoint in WordPress
- Handles auth between WC store and WCPOS app
- Auto-deployed to WordPress.org via GitHub Actions

WordPress hooks documented at: https://wcpos.github.io/woocommerce-pos
